column9: corn thresher is a farming machine used to separate corn kernels from the cob efficiently. It operates by using a rotating drum or spikes that strip the kernels while leaving the cob intact.

column9: A water pump is a mechanical device designed to move water from one location to another efficiently. It is commonly used in agriculture, construction, residential water supply, and industrial applications. Water pumps operate using centrifugal force or positive displacement mechanisms, depending on the type.
